title: Alien Visitor #1 - 3D Printed Sci-Fi Desk Decor
description: Meet your new extraterrestrial companion! This quirky alien visitor features a classic grey design with oversized almond eyes and an endearing pose. Perfect for sci-fi enthusiasts, X-Files fans, or anyone who believes we're not alone. Makes an out-of-this-world gift or conversation piece for your desk, shelf, or anywhere that needs a touch of the unknown.

title: Alien Visitor #2 - 3D Printed Pondering Alien Figurine
description: Caught in a moment of deep contemplation, this pondering alien sits with chin resting thoughtfully on hand - perhaps wondering about the mysteries of the universe, or just what's for dinner on their home planet. A unique twist on the classic grey alien, this philosophical figure adds personality and intrigue to any space.
notes: Eyes will be black on actual print (unless specified in order notes)

title: Alien Visitor #3 - 3D Printed Curious Alien Figurine
description: This inquisitive little being leans in with wide-eyed wonder, as if discovering Earth for the very first time. With an expression of pure curiosity and childlike amazement, Alien Visitor #3 captures that magical moment of first contact. Whether peering at your keyboard or investigating your coffee mug, this curious cosmic traveler brings a sense of wonder to any space.
notes: Eyes will be black on actual print (unless specified in order notes)

title: Alien Visitor #4 - 3D Printed Zen Alien Figurine
description: Find your inner peace with this serene extraterrestrial sage. Alien Visitor #4 sits in tranquil meditation, having mastered the art of cosmic mindfulness across countless light-years of travel. This peaceful figure radiates calm energy and makes the perfect companion for your desk, meditation corner, or anywhere you need a reminder to breathe and center yourself.
notes: Eyes will be black on actual print (unless specified in order notes)

title: 3D Printed Brain Lamp - Unique Anatomical Light from Brain Scan
description: Unique anatomical light modeled directly from real MRI scan data. Soft internal lighting creates a mesmerizing effect.
materials: PLA Plastic, E6000 Adhesive, Rechargeable LED unit, Remote Control, Charging Cable
notes: Made to order. Brain is clear/translucent white unless otherwise specified.

title: Life-Size 3D Printed Brain - Realistic Anatomical Model
description: This life-size anatomical brain model captures every fold, fissure, and convolution of the human brain with stunning accuracy. Created from actual MRI scan data, it's perfect for medical students, neuroscience enthusiasts, psychology professionals, or anyone fascinated by the most complex organ in the known universe.

title: Magic Lamp - Incense Holder - 3D Printed
description: Grant yourself the gift of ambiance with this enchanting magic lamp incense holder. Inspired by the legendary genie lamp, smoke rises mysteriously from the spout as your favorite incense burns inside - creating the illusion of mystical vapors escaping from within. A mesmerizing centerpiece for meditation, relaxation, or adding a touch of Arabian Nights magic to any room.

title: Articulated Asian-Style Dragon - 3D Printed Fantasy Creature
description: This majestic Asian-style dragon flows with the grace of ancient mythology. Fully articulated with flexible joints throughout its serpentine body, you can pose it coiled around objects, stretched out in flight, or curled in rest. Each scale and whisker is intricately detailed, bringing centuries of Eastern dragon lore to life on your desk or shelf.

title: 3D Printed Articulated Skeletal Dragon
description: Unearthed from a dragon's graveyard, this skeletal dragon reveals the fearsome anatomy beneath the scales. Every bone, rib, and vertebra is meticulously detailed, and the fully articulated joints let you pose this undead creature in menacing stances. Perfect for fantasy fans, D&D enthusiasts, or anyone who appreciates the darker side of dragon lore.

title: 3D Printed Articulated Steampunk Dragon
description: Where Victorian engineering meets mythical beast! This steampunk dragon features gears, pistons, and riveted armor plating that make it look like it flew straight out of a Jules Verne novel. Fully articulated for dynamic posing, it's a must-have for steampunk enthusiasts, makers, and anyone who dreams of mechanical marvels.

title: Rock Dragon - 3D Printed - flexible/articulated
description: Born from the mountains themselves, this elemental dragon features rugged stone-like texturing that makes it look like it could crumble into boulders at any moment - but don't worry, the flexible articulated joints let you pose this earth-born beast however you like. A unique take on dragon design for geology buffs and fantasy fans alike.

title: Dragon - Flexi 3D Printed Articulated
description: This friendly flexi dragon is endlessly fun to handle! With smooth, flowing articulation from head to tail, it slithers and coils in your hands like a living creature. Great as a desk fidget, a gift for dragon lovers of all ages, or simply as a delightfully tactile piece of moving art.

title: Forest Godess Planter/Pen/Pencil/Brush Holder
description: Let nature's guardian watch over your plants or art supplies! This mystical forest goddess features flowing organic textures reminiscent of ancient trees and woodland spirits. Use it as a succulent planter, pen holder, or brush organizer - the matching tray catches any overflow. A beautiful blend of the natural and the magical.

title: Retro-Style 3D Printed Rocket Ship Launch - Desk Toy or Cake Topper
description: Blast off to nostalgia with this retro-futuristic rocket ship! Inspired by the golden age of space exploration and 1950s sci-fi, this charming rocket features classic fins, riveted panels, and that unmistakable atomic-age optimism. Perfect as a desk toy, cake topper for space-themed parties, or a gift for anyone who still dreams of the stars.

title: Dragon Egg - 3D Printed
description: What ancient creature slumbers within? This beautifully textured dragon egg features meticulously detailed scales that catch the light and fire the imagination. Display it in a place of honor and let visitors wonder what mythical beast might one day hatch. A must-have for fantasy collectors and Game of Thrones fans.

title: Midgard Serpent - Jormungandr - Stylized 3D Printed Sea Serpent
description: From the depths of Norse mythology rises Jormungandr, the World Serpent! This stylized sea serpent captures the power and mystery of the legendary beast said to encircle Midgard. With a stunning two-color design that highlights every scale and fin, it's a striking piece for mythology enthusiasts and Viking fans alike.

title: Oni Devil - 3D Printed Desk or Wall Sculpture
description: This fearsome Oni brings the power of Japanese folklore to your space. With its fierce expression, prominent horns, and intricate detailing, this devil mask commands attention whether displayed on your desk or mounted on your wall. In Japanese tradition, Oni serve as protectors who ward off evil - let this guardian watch over your domain.

title: Behind Oni Wall Mask - 3D Printed
description: Go beyond the surface with this intriguing Oni wall mask that reveals what lies beneath. This larger, highly detailed piece captures the full intensity of the Japanese demon with exquisite craftsmanship. Mount it prominently to create a powerful focal point that sparks conversation and protects your space with ancient mystical energy.

title: Gorilla - Flexible 3D Printed
description: This mighty silverback demands respect! With fully articulated joints, you can pose this powerful gorilla in countless positions - beating its chest, lounging thoughtfully, or ready for action. The detailed musculature and expressive face capture the majesty of these incredible primates. Perfect for animal lovers and anyone who appreciates nature's strength.

title: Female Face Fidget Toy - Pixels - 3D Printed
description: Part art, part stress relief, all satisfaction! This unique fidget toy features a pixelated female face design that's oddly mesmerizing to manipulate. Keep your hands busy during calls, while thinking through problems, or just when you need a moment of tactile calm. A conversation-starting desk companion unlike anything else.

title: Robot Hand Controller Holder - 3D Printed
description: Give your controller the grip of the future! This robotic hand holds your gamepad in mechanical fingers when you're not playing, adding serious sci-fi style to your gaming setup. The detailed mechanical design looks like it came straight from a cyberpunk workshop. Your controller deserves better than lying on the floor - give it a proper mechanical throne.

title: Futuristic Cityscape Head Planter or Pencil Holder - 3D Printed
description: Where urban imagination meets botanical beauty! This head planter features a mind-bending futuristic cityscape design, as if skyscrapers and structures have grown from pure thought. Perfect for succulents, air plants, or your favorite pens and pencils. The matching tray completes the look while protecting your surfaces.

title: Geared Heart - 3D Printed - Fully Assembled
description: Love meets engineering in this stunning mechanical heart! Real working gears mesh together in an intricate display of mechanical artistry. Turn the gear and watch the heart come alive with motion. A perfect gift for engineers, romantics, steampunk enthusiasts, or anyone who appreciates the beauty of mechanisms. Arrives fully assembled and ready to display.

title: Life Size BRICK BLOCK Flowers - 3D Printed
description: Build your own everlasting garden! These life-size flowers feature a charming brick-block aesthetic that fans of building toys will instantly recognize. Unlike real flowers, these never wilt, need no water, and bring a playful pop of color to any space. Collect different varieties to create your own pixelated bouquet.

title: Dragon Egg Lamp - Cordless Rechargeable Remote Controlled
description: Watch your dragon egg glow with inner fire! This enchanting lamp features a beautifully scaled dragon egg design with a color-changing LED light inside. Use the remote to cycle through colors, set the mood, or find the perfect hue to match your lair. Cordless and rechargeable, place it anywhere without worrying about cords. The dragon inside seems almost ready to hatch...
materials: PLA Plastic, LED unit, Remote Control

title: BRICK BLOCK Flowers - Life Size - 3D Printed - Flower Only
description: Start small or add to your collection! This single brick-block style flower brings nostalgic charm at an affordable price. Mix and match different colors and types to build your own custom bouquet that never needs watering. Perfect for a desk accent, small gift, or testing the waters before committing to a full arrangement.

title: KIT-Zelda - Master Sword - Breath of the Wild - 3D Printed
description: Forge your own legend! This DIY kit contains all the pieces to assemble the iconic Master Sword from The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild. Experience the satisfaction of building this legendary blade yourself, then display it proudly as a testament to your heroic craftsmanship. A must-have for any true Zelda fan's collection.

title: Brick Block Style Collapsible Lightsaber - 3D Printed
description: The Force meets the brick! This collapsible lightsaber combines the charm of brick-block aesthetics with the thrill of Star Wars. A flick of the wrist extends the blade from the hilt - just like the real thing, but blockier. Perfect for fans who grew up loving both building blocks and a galaxy far, far away.

title: 3D Printed Demon Rhino Monster - Ushi - Articulated Fantasy Creature
description: Meet Ushi - a fearsome demon rhino that emerged from the darkest corners of fantasy imagination! This articulated creature features massive horns, armored hide, and a presence that commands attention. Pose this monstrous beast however you like thanks to its flexible joints. A striking collectible for fans of creatures that go bump in the night.

title: Octopus - 3D Printed - Articulated (Floppy Joints)
description: Eight arms of pure fidget satisfaction! This articulated octopus features wonderfully floppy joints that let each tentacle flow and dangle naturally. Pick it up and watch the arms cascade; pose it wrapped around objects or draped dramatically. Equal parts sea creature, stress toy, and desk sculpture - it's irresistibly tactile.

title: 3D Printed Rocket Ship - Retro Space Desk Toy or Cake Topper
description: Houston, we have a charmer! This retro-style rocket captures the optimistic spirit of the space age with its classic fins and streamlined design. Display it on your desk as a daily reminder to reach for the stars, or use it as an unforgettable cake topper for space-themed celebrations. Small enough to fit anywhere, bold enough to make a statement.

title: Foo Lion Statue/Sculpture - 3D Printed
description: Guard your space with ancient Chinese tradition! These majestic Foo Lions (also called guardian lions or shi) have protected temples, palaces, and homes for centuries. With fierce expressions and regal postures, they ward off negative energy while adding an air of timeless elegance. Display one or a pair to honor this powerful tradition.

title: 3D Printed Alien Pilot in Sci-Fi Hover Pod
description: First contact just got stylish! This futuristic collectible features an alien pilot cruising in their personal hover pod, ready to explore your planet. The sleek sci-fi design combines retro UFO aesthetics with modern flair. A must-have for fans of designer toys, extraterrestrial visitors, and anything that defies gravity.

title: 3D Printed Castle - Inspired by Germany Iconic Castles
description: Bring fairytale magic to your shelf! Inspired by the iconic castles of Germany, this detailed miniature captures soaring spires, romantic turrets, and storybook charm. Whether you're a fan of European architecture, Disney-style fantasy, or simply appreciate beautiful craftsmanship, this castle makes a stunning display piece that transports you to another world.

title: Dragon Egg Box/Jar/Container
description: What treasures will you keep in your dragon's egg? This beautifully scaled container opens to reveal a hidden chamber perfect for jewelry, dice, small keepsakes, or whatever precious items deserve a magical home. The detailed scale texture and satisfying lid make it both decorative and functional - a treasure box fit for a dragon's hoard.

title: Alien Hand Video Game Controller Holder
description: Let E.T. hold your controller! This quirky alien hand reaches up to cradle your gamepad with three long extraterrestrial fingers. It's the perfect blend of sci-fi style and practical function - keeping your controller safe, visible, and ready for your next gaming session. A fun conversation piece that any gamer or alien enthusiast will love.

title: Adorable Octopus Buddy - 3D Printed in Multiple Colors
description: Meet your new eight-armed best friend! This adorable little octopus features big expressive eyes and a charm that's impossible to resist. Available in a rainbow of colors to match any mood or decor. Small enough to perch anywhere, cute enough to make you smile every time you see it. Collect them all!

title: 3D Printed Sugar Skull
description: Celebrate life and honor tradition with this stunning sugar skull! Inspired by Dia de los Muertos (Day of the Dead), this intricately detailed skull features the iconic floral and decorative patterns of the Mexican tradition. A beautiful way to remember loved ones, decorate for Halloween, or add meaningful art to your space year-round.

title: 3D Printed Rotating Face Planter and Pencil Holder - Mix-and-Match Oni Design
description: Express yourself differently every day! This innovative planter features rotating face sections that let you mix and match different Oni expressions - from fierce to playful to serene. Turn the segments to create your own unique demon face, or let your plants grow wild from its head. Interactive art meets functional design.

title: 3D Printed Dragon Egg - Game of Thrones Inspired Decor
description: Claim your birthright! This dragon egg captures the iconic look of the eggs from Game of Thrones with its distinctive scaled texture and regal presence. Choose your house colors or go with classic dragon hues. Display it on a stand (sold separately) and let visitors wonder what magnificent creature might emerge. Winter may be coming, but so is your dragon.

title: 3D Printed Celtic Skull - Decorative Skull Sculpture
description: Ancient Celtic artistry meets mortality in this mesmerizing skull sculpture. Intricate knotwork patterns flow across the surface, telling stories of eternity and the interconnected nature of all things. A powerful piece for fans of Celtic heritage, tattoo art, or anyone drawn to symbols that bridge the mystical and the mortal.

title: 3D Printed Dragon Wine Goblet - Game of Thrones Inspired
description: Drink like a Targaryen! This dramatic dragon wine goblet features a coiling dragon design that transforms your drink into a statement. The stem rises from dragon scales while the creature wraps protectively around your chalice. Perfect for themed parties, display, or making every sip feel like a feast in Westeros. (Decorative display piece.)

title: Mechanical King Kong - Full Articulated and Poseable - Giant Robot Ape Kit
description: Build your own mechanical king of the jungle! This impressive kit assembles into a fully articulated giant robot ape, combining the raw power of Kong with mechanical engineering. Every joint moves, every pose is possible - from chest-beating triumph to protective crouch. A challenging build with an epic payoff for fans of kaiju, mechs, and the eighth wonder of the world.

title: Rocket Ship - Blasting Off - 3D Printed - Fully Assembled
description: 3... 2... 1... Liftoff! This dynamic rocket ship captures the thrilling moment of launch, complete with billowing exhaust plume frozen in time. Fully assembled and ready to display, it brings the excitement of space exploration to your desk or shelf. The white smoke plume contrasts beautifully with your choice of rocket color - customize your mission!

title: 3D Printed Chinese Dragon Wine Bottle Holder - Fantasy Decor
description: Let an ancient dragon guard your finest vintage! This majestic Chinese dragon coils around your wine bottle with serpentine grace, its whiskers flowing and scales gleaming. A stunning blend of Eastern mythology and modern bar decor that transforms any bottle into a centerpiece worthy of an emperor's table.

title: 3D Printed Bear Wine Bottle Holder - Rustic Cabin Decor
description: This friendly bear has found something better than honey! Perfect for cabin retreats, rustic kitchens, or anyone who loves woodland charm, this bear wine holder cradles your bottle with ursine enthusiasm. A delightful gift for nature lovers, wine enthusiasts, or anyone who appreciates a good bear hug for their beverages.

title: 3D Printed Stiletto High Heel Wine Bottle Holder - Chic Bar Decor
description: Wine with a side of fabulousness! This sassy stiletto heel wine holder brings high-fashion flair to your bar or kitchen. The elegant high heel design makes any bottle look runway-ready. Perfect for bachelorette parties, fashion-forward friends, or anyone who believes life's too short for boring wine storage.

title: 3D Printed Octopus Wine Bottle Holder - Nautical Decor Gift
description: Release the kraken... of good taste! This magnificent octopus wraps its tentacles around your wine bottle with deep-sea elegance. title: Alien Wine Bottle Holder - 3D Printed in Multiple Colors
description: Your wine collection just got abducted - in the best way! This curious alien visitor has traveled across the galaxy and discovered Earth's finest invention: wine. Watch as it lovingly presents your bottle with those classic extraterrestrial features. A must-have for sci-fi fans who appreciate the finer things, available in an array of otherworldly colors.
